      "instruction": "<p>Once the<strong> </strong>onion has softened, add your <strong>arborio rice </strong>and <strong>chopped garlic </strong>to the pan with your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Add a generous grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in oil</p>",
