    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the risotto has had 20 min, add the<strong> drained sweetcorn</strong> and <strong>smoked basa pieces</strong> to the pan and cook for 5-10 min further or until the basa is cooked through, all of the stock is absorbed and the rice is tender</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Once cooked, stir through<strong> half </strong>your<strong> grated Italian hard cheese </strong>and most of the <strong>chives </strong>(save the rest for garnish!)<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>smoked basa & sweetcorn risotto</strong></p>",
